  <h1 class="gd-h1">What Is Heliskiing?</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Heliskiing trades the chairlift for a helicopter, opening a mountain range no cable or road can reach. This first chapter of the guide explains what the sport actually is, how a day unfolds, and why the Troll Peninsula of North Iceland has become one of its most compelling stages. If you would rather start with the practicalities, browse <a href="/packages">the packages</a>.</p>
</div></section>
